<dt class="postheader">
主题: <strong>Re: 【LOWG】魅魔女神诺缇酷拉-艺术，流亡，午夜的女神（混乱中立）</strong><br>
作者: <strong>红雾的爱泽妮</strong> 于 <strong>2019-09-02, 周一 00:36:48</strong>
<dd class="postbody">
<span style="font-size: 24pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>救赎女皇诺缇酷拉 THE REDEEMER QUEEN（《暴君魔爪ap第六本附录》）</strong></span><br><hr /><span style="font-size: 24pt;" class="bbc_size"><em>世人眼光能奈你何？遵从本心，做你自己，为你的人生作出决定。 但请铭记于心 - 你并非孤身一人。----超越午夜</em></span><br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size">艺术、流放、午夜的女神<br>阵营 CN<br>领域： 手艺领域, 混乱领域, 黑暗领域, 旅行领域, 虚空领域 (Pathfinder RPG Bestiary 6 319)<br>子域： 探索子域 APG , 孤寂子域 ISG , 月子域 ISG , 暗夜子域 APG , 狂欢子域 ISG , 滑稽领域 ISG<br>神选武器：匕首<br>圣徽：戴着七尖王冠微笑的月亮<br>神选动物：蝙蝠<br>神圣色彩：蓝、白 <br>信仰中心：新瑟西隆 ，瓦瑞西亚<br>国度： 登神的恶魔领主<br>服从仪典：在一个僻静的地方花一个小时制作一件艺术品。 如果您的工作时间从午夜开始，结束或包括午夜，您的艺术主题取决于您，除此之外，你的艺术创造必须以某种方式包含午夜的概念。 当你不与盟友相邻时，你的AC和所有豁免检定都会获得+1士气加值。</span><br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><em>传音者神恩</em></span><br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size">1、避世（sp）渐隐术3/day，隐形术2/day或者回避侦测1/day<br>2、救赎之种（Sp）每天一次，你可以对异界生物进行特殊的接触攻击。 如命中，异界生物变得恍惚<br>一轮，因为它突然意识到它不需要遵循其同类的思想道德这一事实 - 它可以选择除了传统行为之外的其他选择。 同时异界生物也必须成功进行意志豁免检定（DC = 10 + 1/2你的HD+你的魅力修正）否则对你友好，如同受到魅惑怪物的影响; 在这种情况下，即使魅惑效果被消除或无效，恍惚效果仍持续1d4 + 1轮。 只要有时间，你就可以帮助异界生物找到一条超越其阵营的新道路，GM决定这种努力的时间和潜在的成功率。<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;这个效果相当于一个7环影响心灵的法术。<br>3、假死（Su）每天一次，当你被伤害降低到负生命值时，你会被减少到1点并受到假象术<br>（施法者等级等于你角色等级）的影响。 这个法术造成的幻影分身外观上是你的尸体。</span><br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><em>颂教者神恩</em></span><br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size">1、艺者精进（sp）：匠人祝福3/日 ，塑木术2/日或 强效幻影1/日<br>&nbsp;2: 迅速造物Swift Creation (Sp)每天一次作为标准动作，你可以召唤一个物体存在于你附近。 以这种方式创造的物体在外观上总是具有艺术性 - 除此之外这种类法术的能力如同强效造物术一样。<br>3、 召唤魔像（sp）Summon Sculpture：每天一次，您可以召唤一个魔像来服侍你。<br>&nbsp;这可以作为召唤怪物IX，但你只能选择召唤一个钢铁魔像（iron golem），1d3石魔像（stone golems）或1d4 + 1个水晶魔像（glass golems）B2。 </span><br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><em>卫道者神恩</em></span><br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"> 1、午夜恩典（sp）克敌机先3/day、猫之优雅2/day 或锐锋术1/day<br>2、曲尾匕舞（EX）：你会长出一条弯曲灵活的尾巴（如果你已经有一条尾巴，你会长出第二条尾巴）。 这条尾巴很容易操纵并且能够操纵和抓握轻小物体，但除了挥舞（wielding）匕首之外，它不能像手一样进行精细的手工操作。 当你进行全回合攻击时，你可以使用这种带有尾部的匕首进行额外的攻击。 当你这样做时，你将此攻击作为主要天武攻击，将你的敏捷调整值添加到任何造成的伤害（额外增加你可能从力量中获得的任何调整值），并且可以攻击到距离比你的基础触及大5尺的范围。 确定用你手中持有的武器进行攻击的罚值时以这种方式用你的尾巴挥舞匕首并不算作双武器战斗。<br>在你没有进行全回合攻击的任何一轮中，但你可以用这个尾巴挥动匕首，它会对你选择的相邻敌人进行一次攻击 - 如果它击中，它不会造成任何伤害，但会分散敌人的注意力，你的AC对该目标获得+2环境加值。 你无法以任何其他方式使用这种带有匕首的尾部进行攻击，包括作为投掷武器。<br>3、午夜复兴（Su）每夜午夜，你都会得到医疗术和高等复原术的好处（两者施法者等级都等于你的角色等级）。</span><br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><em>设计师关于诺缇酷拉的其他内容</em></span><br><hr />https://paizo.com/threads/rzs2l7ns&amp;page=1531?Ask-James-Jacobs-ALL-your-Questions-Here<br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size">设计师：在正义之怒中对巴菲蒙特Baphomet的期望是他被击败但没有被永远杀死; 他很可能被PC杀死，但他的深渊复活使他恢复了生机，他躲藏了一年，所以他可以避免真正的死亡。这也是为什么巴菲蒙特Baphomet没有追逐PC进入正义之怒的最后一次冒险或者继续成为PC敌人的一个很好的理由。<br>在戴斯卡利Deskari的例子中，他也被PC击败，而深渊复活让他恢复了生机，但正如“蝗虫之城”第57页所建议的那样，当PC击败Deskari时，世界之殇的关闭扰乱了他与他的深渊的联系。<br><br>那么说，我认为他死的真正原因是因为诺缇酷拉在PC击败他之后突然进入并完成了杀死恶魔领主的壮举。这是一个很好的结局，让戴斯卡利Deskari的暗杀成为诺缇酷拉杀死的最后一个恶魔领主，并且在PC杀死他之后让她在幕后杀死他，防止抢夺玩家的胜利感。<br><br>无论如何......是的，戴斯卡利Deskari已经死了，巴菲蒙特Baphomet还活着 - “缓刑”已经过去了一年，他的深渊复活能力让他又活蹦乱跳了。</span>
<dt class="postheader">
主题: <strong>Re: 【LOWG】魅魔女神诺缇酷拉-艺术，流亡，午夜的女神（混乱中立）</strong><br>
作者: <strong>红雾的爱泽妮</strong> 于 <strong>2019-09-02, 周一 15:25:39</strong>
<dd class="postbody">
原文：<br>THE REDEEMER QUEEN<br>Goddess of artists, exiles, and midnight<br>Alignment CN<br>Domains Artifice, Chaos, Darkness, Travel, Void (Pathfinder RPG Bestiary 6 319)<br>Subdomains Exploration APG , Isolation ISG , Moon ISG , Night APG , Revelry ISG , Whimsy ISG<br>Favored Weapon dagger<br>Holy Symbol moon with a pair of smirking lips and a seven-pointed crown<br>Sacred Animal bat<br>Sacred Colors blue, white <br>Centers of Worship New Thassilon, Varisia Nationality risen demon lord<br>&nbsp;Obedience Spend an hour in a secluded location while crafting a work of art. If your hour of work begins at, ends at, or includes the stroke of midnight, then the subject of your art is up to you. Otherwise, your art must include the concept of midnight in some way. When you aren’t adjacent to an ally, gain a +1 morale bonus to your AC and on all saving throws.<br>EVANGELIST BOONS<br>1: Avoid Society (Sp) vanish APG 3/day, invisibility 2/day, or nondetection 1/day<br>2: Seed of Redemption (Sp) Once per day, you can make a special touch attack against an outsider. On a hit, the outsider becomes staggered for 1 round as it suddenly becomes aware of the fact that it need not follow the ethos and morals of its kind— that it can choose options other than the traditions of its ilk. The outsider must also succeed at a Will saving throw (DC = 10 + 1/2 your Hit Dice + your Charisma modifier) or become favorably disposed toward you, as if affected by charm monster; in this case the stagger effect persists for 1d4+1 rounds, even if the charm effect is dispelled or negated. Given time, you may be able to convert the outsider from its ways and help it find a new path beyond its alignment, although the GM should adjudicate the time and potential success of such an endeavor.<br>&nbsp;This effect is the equivalent of a 7th-level mind-affecting spell.<br>3: False Demise (Su) Once per day, when you are reduced to negative hit points by damage, you are instead reduced to 1 hit point and affected by a mislead spell (caster level equals your character level). The illusory double created by the spell appears to be your dead body.<br>EXALTED BOONS<br>1: Artist’s Flourish (Sp) crafter’s fortune APG 3/ day, wood shape 2/day, or major image 1/day<br>2: Swift Creation (Sp) Once per day as a standard action, you can conjure an object into existence in your vicinity. Objects created in this fashion are always artistic in appearance— otherwise this spell-like ability functions as major creation.<br>&nbsp;3: Summon Sculpture (Sp) Once per day, you can summon a construct to do your bidding.<br>&nbsp; This functions as summon monster IX, but you can only choose to summon one iron golem, 1d3 stone golems, or 1d4+1 glass golems B2 .<br>SENTINEL BOONS<br>1: Midnight’s Grace (Sp) true strike 3/day, cat’s grace 2/day, or keen edge 1/day<br>2: Sinuous Daggerplay (Ex) You grow a sinuous tail (if you already have a tail, you grow a second one). This tail is prehensile and capable of manipulating and holding small objects, but cannot perform fine manual work as if it were a hand, with the exception of wielding a dagger. When you make a full attack, you can make an additional attack with this tail-wielded dagger. When you do so, you resolve this attack as a primary attack, add your Dexterity modifier to any damage dealt (in addition to any modifiers you might have from Strength), and have a reach that is 5 feet greater than your base reach. Wielding a dagger with your tail in this way does not count as two-weapon fighting for the purposes of determining penalties to attacks made with weapons wielded in your hands.<br>In any round during which you don’t make a full attack but you wield a dagger with this tail, it makes a single attack against an adjacent enemy of your choice—if it hits, it deals no damage but distracts the foe enough so that you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your Armor Class against that target. You cannot attack with this tail-wielded dagger in any other way, including as a thrown weapon.<br>3: Midnight Rejuvenation (Su) Every night at midnight, you gain the benefits of a heal spell and a greater restoration spell (both resolve at a caster level equal to your character level).
